org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.ace

Interface AceFileVisitorCallback.AceFileVisitorMemento

  • Enclosing interface:
    AceFileVisitorCallback

    public static interface AceFileVisitorCallback.AceFileVisitorMemento
    AceFileVisitorMemento is a marker interface that AceFileParser instances can use to "rewind" back to the position in its ace file in order to revisit portions of the ace file. AceFileVisitorCallback.AceFileVisitorMemento should only be used by the AceFileParser instance that generated it.
    Author:
    dkatzel
